extends layouts/main

block content
  .about-container
    .container
      h1 About CivicaLex
      
      .about-section
        h2 Our Mission
        p CivicaLex is dedicated to making legal information accessible to every Indian citizen. We believe that access to justice begins with access to legal knowledge and resources.
        
      .about-section
        h2 What We Do
        .features-grid
          .feature-box
            h3 Legal Information Access
            p Comprehensive database of Indian laws, acts, and legal procedures
          .feature-box
            h3 Case Management
            p Tools to track and manage legal cases efficiently
          .feature-box
            h3 Petition Services
            p Assistance in drafting and filing legal petitions
          .feature-box
            h3 Document Management
            p Secure storage and organization of legal documents
          .feature-box
            h3 Legal Aid
            p Connecting citizens with legal aid services
          .feature-box
            h3 Legal Awareness
            p Educational resources about rights and legal processes
      
      .about-section
        h2 Our Team
        p CivicaLex is built by a team of legal professionals, technologists, and social activists committed to democratizing access to legal information in India.
      
      .about-section
        h2 Our Vision
        p We envision an India where every citizen has the knowledge and tools to understand and exercise their legal rights, regardless of their economic or social background.
      
      .about-section
        h2 Technology
        p Built with modern web technologies ensuring security, scalability, and ease of use. Our platform prioritizes data privacy and user security.
      
      .about-section
        h2 Contact Us
        p Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you.
